# Query pack template — copy this file to data/seeds/<pack-slug>.tsv
#
# Format:
#   <rank><TAB><query>   — rank is ignored; only the query text is stored
#   <query>              — tab-free lines are treated as plain query text
#
# Rules:
#   - Lines starting with # are comments (skipped)
#   - Blank lines are skipped
#   - The filename stem becomes the pack slug (e.g. hospital-guide-robot.tsv → pack=hospital-guide-robot)
#   - Re-running scripts/init.sh is idempotent (INSERT OR IGNORE)
#
# Examples:
1	展厅机器人哪个品牌好
2	展厅智能机器人推荐
3	企业展厅导览机器人有哪些
